WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:11.000
My grandmother had eight brothers and sisters. She started school when she was 80 years old and left when she was 14.

00:11.000 --> 00:21.000
She didn't go to university. She started work after she left school. She worked very hard in a factory.

00:21.000 --> 00:28.000
She went to work at eight o'clock in the morning and finished at six o'clock in the evening.

00:28.000 --> 00:35.000
She worked six or even seven days a week and had only a few holidays.

00:35.000 --> 00:43.000
She got married when she was 18 and had a baby the following year. She had four children.

00:43.000 --> 00:48.000
She continued working until she was 50 years old.

00:48.000 --> 00:56.000
My mother started school when she was six years old. At 18 she went to university.

00:56.000 --> 01:08.000
She started work when she was 22. She works as a teacher. She works five days a week and has a long holiday in summer and winter.

01:08.000 --> 01:16.000
She got married when she was 24 and had a baby the next year. She only has one child. Me.

01:16.000 --> 01:21.000
My mother will continue to work until she's 55.

